title: Jay and Silent Bob Go Canadian, Eh!
description: Unable to go back and finish high school in America, Jay and Silent Bob head to our friendly neighbor to the north and to Degrassi High.
quote: You’re gonna learn the dual languages of my home and native land and you’re gonna savor my poutine!
altHero: Jay and Silent Bob at the principal’s office
alt1: Alanis Morissette as a very Canadian principal
alt2: Jay and Silent Bob walk down the hallway of a high school
alt3: Silent Bob holds a sword and does a praying mantis in front of a ninja
alt4: Jay and Silent Bob speaking at graduation and everything is covered in Canadian flags
